ezTrack 0.1.0

    Example Godwit Tracking Dataset

    Source: R/godwit_tracks.R
    godwit_tracks.Rd

    A dataset of godwit tracking data used as an example for ezTrack functions.

    Usage

    data(godwit_tracks)

    Format

    A data frame with columns:

    individual.local.identifier

    Unique identifier for each tracked animal

    timestamp

    Datetime of the location fix

    location.long

    Longitude coordinate (WGS84)

    location.lat

    Latitude coordinate (WGS84)

    Source

    Movebank

    Examples

    data(godwit_tracks)
godwit_tracks <- ez_track(godwit_tracks)
#> Detected columns - id: individual.local.identifier, timestamp: timestamp, x: location.long, y: location.lat
